Class UpdateVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.view.UpdateVisitor
  • public class UpdateVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    Visitor class for visiting Socket updates. Currently used updates are:
  • SelectableOptionsUpdate
  • PopupMessageUpdate
  • TotalUpdate
